    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in showroom condition\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior is still spotless. I\u2019m only selling it because I\u2019m downsizing, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
