      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a garage and pampered like a member of the family. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014seriously, it's in absolutely stunning shape! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
