    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, a masterclass in longitudinal balance and high-revving performance. This example features the iconic S54 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS to achieve a linear power band peaking at 8,000 RPM. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is in flawless condition with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, eliminating the common failure points of this platform. This is a mechanically transparent, investment-grade vehicle with pristine paint depth and a meticulous service history covering rod bearing replacement and cooling system overhaul.",
